<subSubSection id="C35330D954604929DC8F9FC3A033F8D4" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BF6635254604929DC8F9FC3A033F8D4" blockId="2.[151,1437,1349,1916]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">
<bibRefCitation id="EFD81EA354604929DC8F9FC3A00BF94A" author="Silveira, A. A." box="[198,379,1736,1762]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" refId="ref5700" refString="Silveira, A. A. (1928) Floralia Montium, vol. 1. Imprensa Official, Bello Horizonte, 426 pp." type="book" year="1928">Silveira (1928)</bibRefCitation>
refers to the specimen 
<emphasis id="B93DBF4054604929DED69FC3A241F949" box="[671,817,1736,1761]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">Silveira 348</emphasis>
, which corresponds to 
<taxonomicName id="4C4918D154604929D8189FC3A4ECF94A" box="[1105,1436,1736,1762]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">
<emphasis id="B93DBF4054604929D8189FC3A415F949" box="[1105,1381,1736,1761]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">Paepalanthus amoenus</emphasis>
var.
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B93DBF4054604929DCDE9FE4A06BF8A0" box="[151,283,1775,1800]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">curralensis</emphasis>
, from a list of his own collections of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4918D154604929DE9C9FE5A20DF8A0" box="[725,893,1774,1800]" class="Liliopsida" family="Eriocaulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Eriocaulaceae</taxonomicName>
. This specimen was found at R and contains a detailed description in Silveira’s handwriting. However, this description has never been published. According to article 32.1 and recommendation 50.1 of the ICBN (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD81EA354604929DF709E37A541F8FE" author="McNeill, J. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Burdet, H. M. &amp; Demoulin, V. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Markhold, K. &amp; Nicolson, D. H. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Silva, J. P. C. &amp; Skog, J. E. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J." box="[825,1073,1852,1878]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51" refId="ref5205" refString="McNeill, J., Barrie, F. R., Burdet, H. M., Demoulin, V., Hawksworth, D. L., Markhold, K., Nicolson, D. H., Prado, J., Silva, J. P. C., Skog, J. E., Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J. (eds.) (2006) International Code of Botanical Nomenclature. Guntner Verlag. Ruggell, 568 pp." type="book" year="2006">
McNeill 
<emphasis id="B93DBF4054604929DFE09E37A296F8FD" box="[937,998,1852,1877]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
), the name must be treated as 
<emphasis id="B93DBF4054604929DCDE9E68A04CF8D4" box="[151,316,1891,1916]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">nomen nudum</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
